      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a solid value for someone looking for dependable transportation without the premium price tag of a showroom model. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some fading in the clear coat on the roof and hood, and a few small door dings. Inside, the cabin is clean but shows typical wear on the driver's seat bolster and some minor staining on the rear carpets. Mechanically, the car starts up reliably and runs well, though it will likely need routine maintenance like new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s an honest, high-mileage driver that still has plenty of life left for the right owner.",
