      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s a total dream. This car is in truly stunning condition\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve pampered it since day one, so it\u2019s super clean and drives perfectly. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and is ready for some new adventures, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat more about it!",
