    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available now is an investment-grade 2008 BMW M3 (E92) Coupe, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 paired with a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. This specimen is mechanically superlative, featuring documented rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service to ensure long-term powertrain integrity. The chassis retains its factory-correct rigidity, utilizing Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and an M Variable Differential Lock for optimal lateral dynamics. The exterior showcases original paint with zero orange peel or rock chips, while the underside remains dry with no fluid seepage from the rear main seal or differential. This is a turn-key, collector-quality example of the only V8-powered M3 ever produced.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
