      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor. This car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its flawless deep-gloss finish and pristine, smoke-free leather interior. The body is laser-straight with zero imperfections, stone chips, or door dings. Mechanically, it is absolute perfection; the engine purrs with effortless power, and the gear shifts are crisp and seamless. Every button, dial, and electronic feature functions flawlessly. Included are the complete original service records, all spare keys, and the factory manuals. This is a rare opportunity to own a preserved masterpiece for the most discerning enthusiast.",
