      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unrivaled caliber. This vehicle has been preserved in showroom condition, reflecting a meticulous maintenance history and an uncompromising standard of care. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, confirms its status as an investment-grade acquisition. We offer this exceptional machine to the discerning driver who demands nothing short of mechanical and aesthetic perfection.",
