    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014stunning inside and out! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s in truly pristine, flawless condition. No scratches, no dents, and it still has that fresh feel. I\u2019m sad to let my pride and joy go, but I know the next owner is going to be obsessed with it. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a look!",
