    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Alpine White. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanical excellence is paramount: the rod bearings have been proactively addressed, the rear subframe is fully reinforced, and the double-VANOS system has been overhauled to ensure precise variable valve timing. The chassis remains taut, retaining its original M-tuned suspension geometry and torque-sensing limited-slip differential. With an immaculate interior and flawless original paint, this M3 offers a pure, high-revving analog experience with an 8,000 RPM redline. No leaks, no codes\u2014just precision German engineering in its finest form.",
